<H3> <TI>   Castro Meets With Friendship Caravan Members </TI></H3>
<H4>   Radio Reports Meeting </H4>
<F P=102> FL1903124194 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1205 
GMT 19 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL1903124194 </F>
<F P=104>  Havana Radio Rebelde Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Commander in Chief Fidel Castro met with members of 
the Friendship Caravan. During the meeting Reverend Lucius 
Walker gave an extensive explanation about the organization of 
the convoy that covered 13 routes through Canada and the United 
States. 

</TEXT>

