<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The presence of Professor Rodrigo Alvarez Cambras in 
Ciudad Bolivar and Puerto Ordaz, Venezuela, is proof of the 
interest on the part of Venezuela's public health leadership in 
developing aspects of holistic and sports medicine. 
  Alvarez Cambras said he had been able to hold exchanges with 
Venezuelan scholars on spinal surgery and [word indistinct] in 
ankle lesion surgery at the Social Security Hospital in Puerto 
Ordaz. 
