mate of Andres Pastrana, the man Colombians are awaiting to 
manage the country's future. I hope with your and all 
Colombians' cooperation this country will continue on the path 
to growth, progress, and optimism, the path offered by our 
ticket. Today, I have the great honor of accepting to accompany 
Andres Pastrana, and I do so with great pride. Thank you. [end 
