<F P=106> [From the "Caracol's 0600 to 0900" newscast] </F>
  [Text] AD/M-19 [19 April Movement Democratic Alliance] 
members of Antonio Navarro's presidential campaign have just 
made the following announcement: Antonio Navarro does not plan 
to withdraw his candidacy. AD/M-19 congressmen, contrary to what 
has been reported in some media, have confirmed their solidarity 
with Antonio Navarro. The AD/M-19 congressmen will meet in Santa 
Fe de Bogota at 0900 today to begin a new course, a new boost to 
