  Jose Cuesta is one of the AD/M-19 leaders proposing Navarro 
give up his candidacy and that Ramon Jimeno should be the 
presidential candidate and Gustavo Petro should be the vice 
presidential candidate for the AD/M-19, but Gustavo Petro has 
said he does not accept Jose Cuesta's proposal and supports 
Antonio Navarro. 

